TTG (Template Task Graph) Copyright and License
================================================

Copyright (c) 2016-2025, The TTG Developers
All rights reserved.

The TTG Developers
------------------

TTG is developed collaboratively by researchers from multiple institutions.
The primary institutional contributors are:

  * Stony Brook University (SBU)
  * University of Tennessee, Knoxville (UTK)
  * Virginia Tech (VT)

Principal Contributors and Institutional Affiliations
-----------------------------------------------------

Based on substantial contributions to the codebase, the principal contributors
and their primary institutional affiliations include:

  Stony Brook University:
    - Robert J. Harrison
    - Joseph Schuchart
    - Poornima Nookala

  University of Tennessee, Knoxville:
    - George Bosilca
    - Thomas Herault

  Virginia Tech:
    - Eduard Valeyev

Additional Contributors
-----------------------

TTG has benefited from contributions by many individuals. For a complete list
of all contributors, please see the git commit history:

    git log --format='%aN <%aE>' | sort -u

or visit: https://github.com/TESSEorg/ttg/graphs/contributors

Funding Acknowledgment
----------------------

The development of TTG has been supported by the National Science Foundation
through the following grants:

  The EPEXA Project:
    - Award 1931387 (Stony Brook University)
    - Award 1931384 (University of Tennessee, Knoxville)
    - Award 1931347 (Virginia Tech)

  The TESSE Project:
    - Award 1450344 (Stony Brook University)
    - Award 1450300 (University of Tennessee, Knoxville)
    - Award 1450262 (Virginia Tech)

