Citation
--------

When referring to TTG in an academic setting, please cite:

  G. Bosilca, R. J. Harrison, T. Herault, M. M. Javanmard, P. Nookala and
  E. F. Valeev, "The Template Task Graph (TTG) - an emerging practical dataflow
  programming paradigm for scientific simulation at extreme scale," 2020 IEEE/ACM
  Fifth International Workshop on Extreme Scale Programming Models and Middleware
  (ESPM2), 2020, pp. 1-7, doi: 10.1109/ESPM251964.2020.00011.

Contact
-------

For questions about TTG, please visit: https://github.com/TESSEorg/ttg
